═══ PERSONALIZATION BADGE ═══
Turkish text: "Bu kitap ${kahraman.isim} için özel olarak üretilmiştir"
Style: Premium gold foil seal (#D4A574) with subtle emboss effect — like a quality certification stamp. Small, bottom-left corner. Makes the book feel SPECIAL and PREMIUM.

═══ BOOK FORMAT (CRITICAL — read carefully) ═══
- This is a THIN FLEXIBLE PAPERBACK — magazine-style, saddle-stitched like a school workbook or activity magazine
- NOT a hardcover book. NOT a thick novel. NO thick spine. NO embossed title. NO hardback rigid board.
