- For this specific render: show as a COMPLETELY FLAT print-ready cover page (2:3 portrait). NO 3D mockup, NO page curl, NO bent corners, NO curved edges, NO wavy paper, NO warp, NO perspective. The cover must sit STRAIGHT and RIGID as if scanned flat. If any corner bends or the page curves, the image is WRONG.
- ABSOLUTELY NOT: hardcover, case-bound, leather, cloth, thick spine, gold-foil embossed title, raised letters`;

  switch (category.visualStyle) {
    case "pixar-3d":
      return `${baseInstructions}

ART STYLE: CINEMATIC 3D Pixar/Disney CGI — like a key frame from a Pixar feature film.
- Stylized 3D CGI (Encanto / Coco / Luca quality — NOT cheap mobile game graphics)
- Character face based on reference photos but Pixar-ified: bigger expressive eyes, softer rounder features, exaggerated emotion
- CINEMATIC SCENE (not flat backdrop): ${firstScene} — render as a FULL 3D WORLD with depth, atmosphere, particles
